South African Competition Commission Seeks to Appeal Sasol, Omnia Decision

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-29T10:57:16Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-29/south-african-competition-commission-seeks-to-appeal-sasol-omnia-decision.html
South Africa ’s  Competition
Commission  said it filed an application for direct access to the
Constitutional Court to reverse a Competition Appeal Court
decision relating to an antritrust ruling involving Omnia 
Fertiliser Ltd., Sasol Chemical Industries Ltd. and  Yara
International ASA (YAR) ’s local unit.  The Competition Commission commented in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
